sentences.sentence: This product supports Multiform MDM (see Resources).
sentences.translation: 此产品支持多形式MDM(见参考资料)。

sentences.sentence: The multiform theater is connected to the southwest leg close to the top.
sentences.translation: 多功能剧场位于西南角，靠近顶部的位置。

sentences.sentence: All were Albert and myself, secretive, busy and multiform in other dimensions of time.
sentences.translation: 那些人是艾伯特和我，隐蔽在时间的其他维度之中，忙忙碌碌，形形色色。
